skdetail:

Invocation Name: multiplication tables
des:
Easy and effective learning method to get children to learn and study multiplication tables.
Childer can learn by listening this whole day by giving commands to Alexa.

As of now we have added tables of 1 to 10.

To start, just say:- Alexa, start Multiplication Tables (this will start table from 1)

To play specific table, just say:- Alexa, ask Multiplication Tables to play table of 1

You can also pause, resume, start over commands!
